Social icons base64
=================

Several social icons as base64 strings

#### Usage

Just include the 'constants.php' file and use a constant as a image source.

```php
<?php require_once('constants.php'); ?>
...
<img src="<?php echo IMG_FACEBOOK; ?>" alt="Facebook" />
<img src="<?php echo IMG_TWITTER; ?>" alt="Twitter" />
<img src="<?php echo IMG_YOUTUBE; ?>" alt="Youtube" />
...
```
